rbnL2vpnCap.name: rbnL2vpnCap

revisions.description: Update DESCRIPTION clause of MODULE-IDENTITY and PRODUCT-RELEASE clause of AGENT-CAPABILITIES.
Added rbnL2vpnCap3 including rbnMplsL2VpnPwScalarGroup, rbnMplsL2VpnStaticPwGroup, rbnMplsL2VpnLdpPwGroup to deprecate rbnMplsL2VpnStaticGroup, rbnMplsL2VpnLdpGroup.
Changed the indexing sequence of L2VPN static and ldp tables. Obsoleted rbnL2vpnCap1, and added rbnL2vpnCap2.

rbnL2vpnCap.contactinfo: Ericsson AB. Postal: 100 Headquarters Dr. San Jose, CA 95134 USA Phone: +1 408 750 5000 Fax: +1 408 750 5599
rbnL2vpnCap.description: The Agent Capabilities for RBN-L2VPN-MIB If this MIB implementation is platform-dependent, the PRODUCT-RELEASE clause contains Ericsson SEOS version and at least one of the following Ericsson product families: [SE] SmartEdge Multi-service Edge Router (MSER) family [SM] SM family of Metro Ethernet Service Transport platforms [SSR] Smart Service Router (SSR) family
